									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch4.p1",
									"fallback": "I'm trying to find this child but so far in vain, they must be in a neighboring realm."
								},
								{
									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch4.p2",
									"fallback": "The story of this child takes a dark turn. On the walls of Helheim, I found traces."
								},
								{
									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch4.p3",
									"fallback": "This gift of immortality, meant to be a blessing, transformed into a curse."
								},
								{
									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch4.p4",
									"fallback": "The eternal child, once described as full of life, has traversed millennia of wars and chaos."
								},
								{
									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch4.p5",
									"fallback": "Unable to die, an eternal witness to our \"game\", they gradually lost their humanity."
								},
								{
									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch4.p6",
									"fallback": "The echoes and rumors now speak of a being consumed by destruction, seeking to ease their madness in chaos."
								},
								{
									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch4.p7",
									"fallback": "The first observer had described them as a child full of life, and seemed to love them, and the child seemed to say they felt protected. Hmm..."
								},
								{
									"translate": "item.yggdrasil.helheim.chronicles.ch4.p8",
									"fallback": "Not surprising, I would probably end up the same if I had no possibility of dying."
